OL,3,CWhich airlines are cancelling flights
OL,4,Cand pushing up prices?
OL,6,FMany airlines have already raised
OL,7,Fchecked bag fees or added fuel
OL,8,Fsurcharges as the global price of jet
OL,9,Ffuel increased from about $99 (#73.31)
OL,10,Fper barrel at the end of February to
OL,11,Fas high as $209 (#154.76) a barrel at
OL,12,Fthe beginning of April.
OL,14,FSo are flight tickets going up and are
OL,15,Fflights being cancelled? ITV News has
OL,16,Fcontacted a number of airlines to find
OL,17,Fout.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
