OL,3,CWhich airlines are cancelling flights
OL,4,Cand pushing up prices?
OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FAir France / KLM
OL,13,FAir France and KLM have increased
OL,14,Fticket prices. For Economy Class
OL,15,Ftickets on long-haul flights, the fare
OL,16,Fincrease is E100 (#86.81) per round
OL,17,Ftrip.
OL,26,@xD@MOk
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/10
