OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1776898985
OL,3,CWhich airlines are cancelling flights
OL,4,Cand pushing up prices?
OL,6,FFor flights to the United States,
OL,7,FCanada, and Mexico, the increase is
OL,8,FE70 (#60.77) per round trip. For short-
OL,9,F and medium-haul Economy Class
OL,10,Fflights, the increase is E10 (#8.68)
OL,11,Fper round trip.
OL,13,FStarting from April 27, KLM will
OL,14,Foperate 80 fewer round-trip flights in
OL,15,Fthe coming month due to rising jet
OL,16,Ffuel costs.
OL,26,@pD@AOkrD@ZOk
