OL,3,CWhich airlines are cancelling flights
OL,4,Cand pushing up prices?
OL,6,FThis represents less than 1% of their
OL,7,Fflights within Europe during that time
OL,8,Fand passengers booked on these flights
OL,9,Fwill be rebooked onto the next
OL,10,Favailable flight.
OL,12,FThey told us they are actively
OL,13,Fmonitoring fuel supply as it affects
OL,14,Fall airlines but there is no
OL,15,Fdisruption at the moment.
OL,17,FA spokesperson said: "The airline will
OL,18,Fwork with its suppliers to secure the
OL,19,Fjet fuel available in line with its
OL,20,Fneeds.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/10
