OL,3,CWhich airlines are cancelling flights
OL,4,Cand pushing up prices?
OL,6,F"We'll keep customers informed and
OL,7,Fprovide timely updates if needed."
OL,9,F20,000 short-haul flights will be
OL,10,Fremoved from the schedule through
OL,11,FOctober due to the price of jet fuel
OL,12,Fwhich has doubled since the outbreak
OL,13,Fof the Iran conflict.
OL,15,FThey say the first 120 daily flight
OL,16,Fcancellations were implemented on
OL,17,FMonday (20 April), effective through
OL,18,Fthe end of May, and affected
OL,19,Fpassengers have been notified.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/10
