OL,3,CWhich airlines are cancelling flights
OL,4,Cand pushing up prices?
OL,6,FFor the flights scheduled in the
OL,7,Fsummer timetable, Lufthansa expects a
OL,8,Flargely stable fuel supply.
OL,10,FAll Lufthansa Group airlines will
OL,11,Fsuspend flights to the Middle East
OL,12,Fthrough April 30.
OL,14,FThey say ticket prices may continue to
OL,15,Fincrease due to the current
OL,16,Fgeopolitical environment.
OL,18,FITV News understands they are
OL,19,Fcurrently seeing no disruption to
OL,20,Fflights and don't plan to make any
OL,21,Fchanges to their flying schedule.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/10
