OL,3,CWhich airlines are cancelling flights
OL,4,Cand pushing up prices?
OL,6,FVirgin Atlantic
OL,8,FThe fuel surcharge for each cabin is
OL,9,Fas follows:
OL,11,FITV News understands there is no
OL,12,Fimmediate risk to supply on their
OL,13,Froutes at present, with flights
OL,14,Foperating as normal.
OL,16,FFly Emirates
OL,18,FThey say they are currently operating
OL,19,Fa reduced number of flights until
OL,20,Ffurther notice.
