OL,3,CWhich airlines are cancelling flights
OL,4,Cand pushing up prices?
OL,6,FQatar Airways
OL,8,FThey say they are expanding their
OL,9,Finternational flight network, with
OL,10,Fservices to over 150 destinations from
OL,11,FJune.
OL,13,FTheir new schedule, valid until mid-
OL,14,FSeptember, introduces new routes and
OL,15,Fincreased frequencies to and from Doha.
OL,17,FA spokesperson for the company told
OL,18,Fus: "It will depend on how the
OL,19,Fsituation evolves; as of now, we are
OL,20,Foperating normally."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/10
